'''香料酒'''（{{lang-en|mulled wine}}）是一種以[[葡萄酒|葡萄酒]]和[[香辛料|香辛料]]為原料的熱飲酒。香料酒一般使用[[紅葡萄酒|紅葡萄酒]]為原料，但也有使用[[白葡萄酒|白葡萄酒]]的香料酒。部分香料酒沒有酒精度數<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/wordofmouth/2010/dec/09/how-to-make-perfect-mulled-wine|title=How to make perfect mulled wine|last=Cloake|first=Felicity|date=9 December 2010|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=5 February 2012|archive-date=2012-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121222061035/http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/wordofmouth/2010/dec/09/how-to-make-perfect-mulled-wine|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在德國和法國等歐洲國家，香料酒是[[萬聖節|萬聖節]]和[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]等秋冬節日時期的必備飲料<ref>{{cite book|last=John|first=J.|title=A Christmas Compendium|year=2005|url=https://archive.org/details/christmascompend0000john_l7t4|publisher=Continuum|pages=[https://archive.org/details/christmascompend0000john_l7t4/page/80 80]|isbn=0-8264-8749-1}}</ref>。由於在加熱過程中會有部分酒精揮發，有時會在香料酒中加入[[蘭姆酒|蘭姆酒]]等[[蒸餾酒|蒸餾酒]]。

